{"tid":1118743,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"我為昨晚開嘅post向獌迷鄭重道歉","createTime":"2019-04-21T14:05:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T17:40:50.000Z","uid":238051,"like":46,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5ad4fa70b875f54edacbceb68a8496f3bdf73cfa","tid":1118743,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T14:05:34.000Z","msg":"事源係咁：<br />\n猁迷要靠獌固然係好柒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1117254\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1117254</a><br />\n<br />\n但經過今晚一役<br />\n我發現我錯了<br />\n仲錯得非常離譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我冇諗過蘇B同獌可以行到呢一步<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>為咗斷送猁嘅英超前程<br />\n不惜提早一場放棄歐聯資格</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢種破釜沉舟嘅氣魄實在令我感到萬分愧疚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望可以同眾獌迷冰釋前嫌<br />\n為阻止猁取得英超嘅共業攜手向前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67b486c0025d51a38b566b49dde040ecf1854380","tid":1118743,"uid":238051,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T16:54:10.000Z","msg":"阿⋯⋯當我冇講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c122d018571524ef04aa8999d6b5b626f53304d","tid":1118743,"uid":200801,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T17:10:18.000Z","msg":"阿記為咗挽留獌都不惜一切"},{"pid":"b211e7be9e7e9607af0fa8b2f3857cdebc98b1b0","tid":1118743,"uid":4187,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6c122d018571524ef04aa8999d6b5b626f53304d","tid":1118743,"uid":200801,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T17:10:18.000Z","msg":"阿記為咗挽留獌都不惜一切"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T17:17:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e8142f6